data.description: Meticulously updated home that's been thoughtfully designed for comfort, convenience, & modern living. Step inside to discover a bright & open layout that immediately feels like home! Beautiful new flooring, updated light fixtures, & bright white doors and trim throughout. Dining space offers backyard views & access through sliding glass doors. Spacious kitchen boasts updated appliances as well as ample counter & storage space. Laundry & updated 1/2 bath are both conveniently located on the 1st floor. 2nd floor offers 3 large bedrooms, including the master w/en'suite bath. Finished basement extends your living space even further, offering endless possibilities as a family room, home gym, or an office for those who work from home. Outside space is private & newly fenced. New roof & HVAC!
